from time import sleep

@loop.on_DATA_PROCESS
def process_data(loop):
    sleep(.1)
    loop.core.double = loop.element*2
    
@loop.on_FORWARD
def update_pg(loop):
    loop.pgbar_description(f"double: {loop.double}")
    
@loop.on_FORWARD
def another_thing_on_forward(loop):
    loop.pgbar_data(dict(a=1))

loop.run()
